# ccmemory: SQLite index is a derived cache, regenerated locally.
# Cover both the legacy ".memory_index.db" name and the current "index.db",
# plus SQLite's WAL/journal sidecars and macOS AppleDouble (._*) files NFS
# creates when the repo is shared between Linux and Mac.
.memory_index.db
.memory_index.db-journal
.memory_index.db-wal
.memory_index.db-shm
index.db
index.db-journal
index.db-wal
index.db-shm
._*
